'''卡梅伦·范德伯格'''（{{lang-en|'''Cameron van der Burgh'''}}，{{bd|1988年|5月25日||}}），出生于[[比勒陀利亚|比勒陀利亚]]，[[南非|南非]][[游泳|游泳]]运动员<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.southafrica.info/news/sport/teamsa-burgh.htm|title=Team SA profile – Cameron van der Burgh|publisher=SouthAfrica.info|accessdate=2012-07-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120812010743/http://www.southafrica.info/news/sport/teamsa-burgh.htm|archivedate=2012-08-12|df=}}</ref>。在[[2012年夏季奧林匹克運動會|2012年奧運會]]上，以破世界紀錄的成績奪得金牌<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.supersport.com/olympics/south-africa/news/120729/Van_der_Burgh_bags_gold_medal|title=SuperSport - Olympics|website=www.supersport.com|access-date=2018-01-11|archive-date=2018-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180111224124/https://www.supersport.com/olympics/south-africa/news/120729/Van_der_Burgh_bags_gold_medal|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在2018年短池世锦赛后宣布退役<ref>{{cite news|url=https://swimswam.com/cameron-van-der-burgh-ends-career-with-textile-wr-gold-medal-in-50-br/|title=CAMERON VAN DER BURGH ENDS CAREER WITH TEXTILE WR, GOLD MEDAL IN 50 BR|work=[[SwimSwam|SwimSwam]]|date=2018-12-16|accessdate=2018-12-17|archive-date=2018-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181217202223/https://swimswam.com/cameron-van-der-burgh-ends-career-with-textile-wr-gold-medal-in-50-br/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

